<view class="page-shell market-page">
  <view class="topbar">
    <view class="brand-row">
      <view class="brand-pin"></view>
      <text class="brand-text">兰州美食</text>
    </view>
    <view class="topbar-actions">
      <view class="icon-button">荐</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section-block">
    <text class="eyebrow">CURATION</text>
    <text class="section-title">精选宣传选题</text>
    <text class="market-intro">这里不再强调限时优惠，而是集中展示适合做宣传扩展、线下体验或专题策展的代表性内容。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="market-grid">
    <view class="market-card card" wx:for="{{products}}" wx:key="_id" bindtap="goToDetail" data-id="{{item._id}}">
      <image src="{{item.coverImage}}" class="market-card-image" mode="aspectFill" />
      <view class="market-card-body">
        <text class="pill pill-secondary">宣传选题</text>
        <text class="market-card-title">{{item.name}}</text>
        <text class="market-copy">适合放入专题策划、文化故事或线下体验路线中，作为宣传展示的延伸内容。</text>
        <text class="market-meta">可结合体验路线继续展开</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>
